'''FAO施瓦茨'''（FAO Schwarz）創建於1862年，是美國歷史最悠久的玩具店之一<ref name="CNBC">{{cite web |url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/46483722/FAO_Schwarz_150_Years_of_Toys |title=FAO Schwarz: 150 Years of Toys |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116081849/http://www.cnbc.com/id/46483722/FAO_Schwarz_150_Years_of_Toys |archivedate=2014-01-16 |df= |accessdate=2017-02-14 }}</ref>，該公司以其獨特的高檔玩具而著稱<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.northjersey.com/news/104925149_Toys__R__Us_has_big_plans_for_luxe_retailer.html|title = Toys 'R' Us has big plans for luxe retailer FAO Schwarz|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121026045852/http://www.northjersey.com/news/104925149_Toys__R__Us_has_big_plans_for_luxe_retailer.html|archivedate = 2012-10-26|accessdate = 2017-02-14}}</ref>。FAO施瓦茨位於紐約市第五大道的旗艦店是紐約著名的旅遊景點之一，但在2015年7月關閉。FAO施瓦茨品牌現在是其創建人FAO施瓦茨家族後裔的財產<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tsdr.uspto.gov/#caseNumber=78759620&caseType=SERIAL_NO&searchType=statusSearch|title=Trademark Status & Document Retrieval: Serial Number 78759620|author=[[United_States_Patent_and_Trademark_Office|United States Patent and Trademark Office]]|accessdate=2012-12-21|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511081924/http://tsdr.uspto.gov/#caseNumber=78759620&caseType=SERIAL_NO&searchType=statusSearch|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但由ThreeSixty Group運營。
